props.allDay: Indicates whether the event spans the entire day.
props.event: The event object associated with this calendar interval.
props.interval: The specific time interval this event is associated with.
props.intervalDivisions: Number of subdivisions within the interval for this event.
props.intervalDuration: Duration of the interval in which this event occurs, in minutes.
props.intervalHeight: Height of the interval in the calendar view, in pixels.
